title: July 2014 Rebel Beats High Intensity Mix (90 Minute)
description:
JULY REBEL BEATS HIGH INTENSITY 90 MINUTE WORKOUT MIX (2014).

Recorded directly from the Rebel Beats app from an iPad to a Macbook Pro using Audio Hijack Pro and an AUX cable. Format to record was 'For internet distribution (high)' MP3, VBR, 128 kbps, Joint Stereo. 

No editing performed by myself, simply a recording of the playlist in order to save mobile data while doing a workout outside of WiFi range. 

Download the Rebel Beats app from either iTunes Store or the Play Store on Android. 

Please seed and comment. Advice welcome.
